<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f5ff;
      color: #4b0082;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .about-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background-color: #f3e6ff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section h1 {
      color: #6a0dad;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #800080;
    }

    .team-section {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .team-section h2 {
      color: #6a0dad;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .team-grid {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .team-member {
      background-color: #f3e6ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      width: 240px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.1);
    }

    .team-member h3 {
      margin: 10px 0 5px;
      color: #4b0082;
    }

    .team-member p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h1>About Our Dental Clinic</h1>
    <p>
        Welcome to <span class="highlight">Diamond Clinic</span> – your trusted partner in oral health.
        We take pride in offering compassionate and professional dental care tailored to your individual needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our clinic provides comprehensive dental services, including general dentistry, cosmetic procedures,
        and preventive care—all delivered in a clean, comfortable setting using modern technology.
      </p>
      <p>
        At BrightSmile, we value patient education, transparency, and long-term results.
        Our mission is to help every patient achieve and maintain a beautiful, healthy smile for life.
      </p>
  </section>

  <section class="team-section">
